  "subject": "Fix: Use == instead of === in upper-constraints.onap.txt",
  "commit_message": "Fix: Use == instead of === in upper-constraints.onap.txt\n\nThe arbitrary equality operator (===) is not compatible with pip's\nconstraint resolution when requirements use >= specifiers. Change\nto == (version matching) for proper pip compatibility.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Iac956409200a2ff9421a10a1b6fac2781b4b77c2\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
